				<div class="l-box pure-u-2-3 justify what-is-docpad">
					<br/>
					<h4 class="content-subhead">What is DocPad?</h4>
					<p>
						DocPad is a next generation web architecture; 
						allowing for content management via the file system, rendering via plugins,
						and static site generation for deployment anywhere.
						It's built with Node.js and Express.js, making it naturally fast and easily extendable.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="pure-u-1-2 auto video-ribbon">
